	<h1 class="title">过山车专业户的中国第一建开工了，地址居然是海盐</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/429696/small/429696.jpg?1453172978" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">杨京楷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-25 08:00:20 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/21176/medium/21176.jpg?1453682971" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


